#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Life Span"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Paṭhamamārapāsasutta → paṭhamapāsasuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | pāsa (1) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn4.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Paṭhamamārapāsasutta"
msgstr "4. Māra’s Snares (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.105"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.235"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "sn4.4:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "sn4.4:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā bārāṇasiyaṃ viharati isipatane migadāye."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Benares, in the deer park at Isipatana."

msgctxt "sn4.4:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn4.4:1.4"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "sn4.4:1.5"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "sn4.4:1.6"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.4:2.1"
msgid "“Mayhaṃ kho, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā yoniso sammappadhānā anuttarā vimutti anuppattā, anuttarā vimutti sacchikatā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I have attained and realized supreme freedom through proper attention and proper effort."

msgctxt "sn4.4:2.2"
msgid "Tumhepi, bhikkhave, yoniso manasikārā yoniso sammappadhānā anuttaraṃ vimuttiṃ anupāpuṇātha, anuttaraṃ vimuttiṃ sacchikarothā”ti."
msgstr "You too should attain and realize supreme freedom through proper attention and proper effort.”"

msgctxt "sn4.4:2.3"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.4:3.1"
msgid "“Baddhosi mārapāsena,"
msgstr "“You’re bound by Māra’s snares,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:3.2"
msgid "ye dibbā ye ca mānusā;"
msgstr "both human and divine."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:3.3"
msgid "Mārabandhanabaddhosi,"
msgstr "You’re bound by Māra’s bonds:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:3.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti."
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Muttāhaṃ → muttohaṃ (bj, s1, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn4.4:4.1"
msgid "“Muttāhaṃ mārapāsena,"
msgstr "“I’m freed from Māra’s snares,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:4.2"
msgid "Ye dibbā ye ca mānusā;"
msgstr "both human and divine."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:4.3"
msgid "Mārabandhanamuttomhi,"
msgstr "I’m freed from Māra’s bonds."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.4:4.4"
msgid "Nihato tvamasi antakā”ti."
msgstr "You’re beaten, terminator!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.4:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."
